title: Remix kits (pack 2: William Orbit)
description:
Here is a collection of various remix kits in the sound formats WAV, AIFF and Ableton Live.

You can use the free software Audacity (http://audacity.sourceforge.net) to open all of these formats.

Have fun playing around with them, and make some great remixes and mashups.


Unfortunately I had to make a ZIP-file of this - the directories contain almost 1200 files, so it was impossible to make a torrent file I could upload to TPB. But I can assure you that it's NOT password protected and contains absolutely no viruses.


And PLEASE seed to at least 1:1 or preferably more. If everybody could seed as much as they download, a torrent will never die!


REMIX KITS:
---
William Orbit - Bubble Universe (remix kit) (aiff + Ableton Live)
William Orbit - Cellcloud (remix kit) (aiff + wav + Ableton Live)
William Orbit - Sea Green (remix kit) (wav + Ableton Live)
William Orbit - Surfin (remix kit) (wav + Ableton Live)
William Orbit - They Live In The Sky (remix kit) (wav + Ableton Live)
